# VHS Demo - AI-Powered Workflow
# Shows Claude Code integration

Output demo/scenarios/04-ai-workflow.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "# AI-Powered Development Workflow"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# Claude Code integration"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "# Custom commands are available via ~/.claude/"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "ls ~/.claude/"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "# Espanso snippets for AI prompts"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "# Type ':explain' to expand to a detailed prompt"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# Example: Code review prompt"
Enter
Type ":review"
Sleep 1s

Type "# AI-assisted git workflow"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "# Use /commit-push for smart commits"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# âœ… AI-enhanced productivity!"
Enter
Sleep 2s
